hymns.lyrics:
Inkos’ ifikil’ emnyango, Eyathwal’ isiphambano;
Manjeabalungileyo, Ba zobutwayiYo.

Iz’bonisoyonk’ im’nyaka, Zithi: sewukhonalapha;
Si zobonamasinyane, Ohleziphakade

Qaphelaniemhlabeni, Inhluphekoazipheli;
Ku zofikauMsindisi, AfeuMkhohlisi.

Khonaezwenielisha, Si zohlalasingabasha;
Abafayobangabhubhi, Kubenaphakade.

Ubusobuzobukana, NoKrestuuMsindisi
Ngizakuthab’ ukumbona uJesuong’uMfeli

Laphang’ bona kalufifi, Ku khon’ okusithayo;
Ngelang’ elingeluvivi, Ngobon’ Okhazim’layo

Ngizojabul’ ukubona, Kon’ okungaziwayo;
Konkekokhanyiswakhona, Ku phel’ okuhluphayo.

Ubusobuzobukana, NaYeuMhlengiwami;
Ngobukananjalomina, NaY’ uMsindisiwami

Nxa icilongo li khala nesikhathi si dlula;
Kofika usuku olumi njalo
Abasindisiweyo ezweni ba zobuthana;
Bebizwa phezulu ngi zobakhona

Ngesikhathi esihle lapho sebevuswa bonke
Ba zoba nesimo esisha bonke
Abakhethiweyo uma sebeqoqelwa khona;
Bebizwa phezulu ngi zobakhona

Ma si yisebenzele iNkosi lize li shone;
Ngothando lweNkosi ma sitshelane,
Si ngafa u zophela umsebenzi wethu lapha
Bebizwa phezulu ngi zobakhona.

Khalisan’ icilongo kakhulu; uJes’ u yeza futhi;
Bonke ba bhekisise phezulu uJes’ u yeza futhi

Memezani naseziqongweni, uJes’ u yeza futhi;
Li za nobukhosi iZinyane, uJes’ u yeza futhi;

Hlokomanini lwandle namaza, uJes’ u yeza futhi;
Qubukani kanjalo zinhlanzi, uJes’ u yeza futhi;

Zi yasitshela iziboniso, uJes’ u yeza futhi;
Nawo umoya u yavunguza, uJes’ u yeza futhi;

Izizwe zonke zi thukuthele, uJes’ u yeza futhi;
Nalo ulwazi futhi lwandile, uJes’ u yeza futhi;

Si yathaba ngothando, Lu yasithabisa;
Lu senza sibe nenqgondo, Kwabanye umusa

Ku khon’ usizi lapha;
Ukufa nezono Ngokuthoba si ngazama, Si zuze umoni

Ekupheleni lapha, Ebuya uJesu;
Sohlabelela ingoma, Yothand’ olukhulu

hymns.chorus:
Inkos’ i thanda bonk’ abaYo, Si fis’ ukuba njengaYo;
Si yathaba ngothando, Lu yasithabisa;
Lu senza sibe nenqgondo, Kwabanye umusa

hymns.lyrics:
Mabutho ka Krestu, Hlomani nonke;
Nilwe noSathani, Isitha kini.
Nang’ uMholi wethu, NguYe uKrestu
‘Nkosi yamakhosi, NguYe uMnqobi

Bhekhanini ‘bandla, Ithuthumela;
Impi ka Sathani, Hlabelelani;
I yesab’ uJesu, U zoyicitha!
Ngezwi lokunqoba, I yokwahlulwa

Hambisan’ okwempi, ‘Bandla leNkosi;
Ma si balingise, Abanqobile
Noko sahlukene, Si semi kanye;
Lon’ ithemba lethu, Linye kuKrestu

Amakhos’ omhlaba, Wonk’ a yabhubha
Keph’ iBandla lethu, Limi kuKrestu;
Qhabo! A lahlulwa, Ngeke ladlula
Wathembis’ uKrestu, Ng’ uMlawuli wethu

Hlanganani bantu, Nebandla lethu
Vumanini nonke, Si bandla linye
Ingoma yodumo, YeNkos’ uqobo
Zi dumise nathi, Nezingelosi

Phinda u ngi hlabelele, Amazw’ okuphila;
Ma ngi bon’ ubuhle bawo, Amazw’ okuphila;
Ngamazwi omusa, A yangifundisa

uJesu wabapha bonke, Amazw’ okuphila;
Soni, u yabizwa, yizwa amazw’ okuphila.
Saphiwa ngesihle, a sisa kuJesu

Ba tshele abantu bonke, amazw’ okuphila;
A leth’ ukuthula wona, NgoJes’ uMsindisi;
U yahlambulula Inhliziyo zethu

Ekupheleni sothokoza, Se si buthana ekhaya;
Si leth’ izithungu zethu, eJerusalem’ eNtsha.

Ingoma za khona zi mnandi, Si yobonga si ngathuli;
S’dums’ iNkosi kamnandi, eJerusalem’ eNtsha.

Ku si lindele ukwethaba, Izindlu zi ningi khona;
Zi lungiswe nguY’ uJesu, eJerusalem’ eNtsha.

Inkumbul’ emnandi, I yabuya kimi;
Ngi sondel’ ekhaya lami, Ku nokoqala.

Eduze k’uBaba, Ezindlini zAkhe;
Ku seduze nesiHlalo, Sobukhosi bAkhe.

Ku duze ngi hambe, Ngi lahle im’thwalo;
Ngi shiy’ inhlupheko lapha, Ng’amukel’ umqhele.

hymns.chorus:
Ngi sondel’ ekhaya lami;
Ngi sondel’ ekhaya namhla
Ku nokokuqala.

hymns.lyrics:
Li khon’ izwe elihl’ impela, Se si bon’ ukukhanya kwalo;
uBaba wethu u khona le, U yasakhela izindlu ke.

Si zohlabel’ ezwen’elihle, Ingoma yeNkosi yakhona;
Inhliziy’ asoze zakhala, Ezweni lelo lokuphumla.

KuBaba wethu ophezulu; Si zohlokomisa ngodumo;
Ngale ‘Sipho esing’ uJesu, Imhla yonk’ abe Sibusiso.

Woza, Mthombo wez’ busiso, Wena wokudunyiswa;
Imifula eyomusa, I fanel’ ukubongwa;
Ngi fundis’ ukuhlonipha, Umusa wAkho kimi;
Eyam’ inhiziyo y’ophe, Ngothando lwAkho kimi.

Mina ngi zozifunela, Ilitshe lokuphepha;
Ngomsa wAkho ngothembela, Ekufiken’ ekhaya;
uJesu wangingenisa, Emhlambini owAkhe
Engozini ngasindiswa, Ngalo igazi lAkhe.

Ngi necala elikhulu, Ngomusa owangipha;
Vumel’ ukulunga Krestu, Ku ngi buyise namhla;
‘Nkosi, ngi ses’ebubini, Ngi thoba phambi kwakho;
Nansi inhliziyo yami, Beka uphawu lwAkho.

Wena Moy’ oiNgcwele, Seku kad’ u lindile,
Ngesandla ma ngi holwe, Mina mhambi ehlane;
Okhathele a bonge Izwi loduduzayo;
Nyenyeza, "Mhambi woza, Ngokuqondis’ ekhaya"

Mhlobo Wen’ osizayo, U yathand’ ozamayo,
U ngasishiyi lapha, Kakhulu si yesaba,
Nxa izulu liduma, NgakuWe, ngokweyama;
Nyenyeza, "Mhambi woza, Ngokuqondis’ ekhaya"

Nkosi yethu enkulu, Si qondise phezulu,
Ngokukhuleka kwethu, Noma amabiz’ ethu;
A khon’ ezulwini na? Izwi li yaphendula:
"Mhambi, mhambi, woza la, Ngokuqondis’ ekhaya"

Into engiyifisayo, Indlela yam’eqondile;
Nezilingo zi yashisa, Ng’hlambulule, ng’hlambulule.

Nxa ngi bona ukukhanya, Ngi yathaba emoyeni;
Ngi fun’ inhliziyo entsha Kuhle kimi, kuhle kimi.

Ngi fis’ ukudel’ okubi, Ngi nomthwalo, se ngi file;
Ubuhle kimina buphi? Ngi ngcolile, ngi ngcolile.

Uma kuthe lenhliziyo, Ya thand’ ukukulandela;
Ng’enze ngibe ngophilayo Ngibe ngcwele, ngibe ngcwele.

Ngi zulile kude, Nkosi,
Se ngi yabuya
Ngi dinwe yizono zami
Nkosi, ngi yeza

Kade ngi cita im’nyaka, Se ngi yabuya;
Manje, se ngi yaphenduka Nkosi, ngi yeza .

Ngi dinwe ukulahleka, Se ngi yabuya;
Ngi themba ilizwi lAkho, Nkos, ngi yeza.

Ngi ncenga ngokukwethemba, Se ngi yabuya;
uJesu wafela mina, Nkosi ngi yeza.

Nkosi, hlanzisisa mina, Se ngi yabuya;
Ma ngi bemhlope njengeqhwa, Nkosi, ngi yeza.

Lowo ozwayo maka memeze;
Ivangeli ma li zungeze izwe.
Lapho ku khon’ abantu ku menyezwe,
Othandayo mak’ eze!

Wena ozayo sheshisa phela;
Umnyango u savuliwe, wongena.
uJesu u thi: "Ngi yiNdlela mina";
Othandayo mak’ eze

Low’ ovumayo nas’ is’thembiso;
Kuy’ osithandayo se si me njalo.
Si yiMpilo enhle eme phakade;
Othandayo mak’ eze!

Ngi ngagezwa ng’ubani? Ng’uJesu ngegazi lAkhe.
Ngi ngahlanzeka njani? Muhlophe ngegazi lAkhe.

Ngi funa ukugezwa: Egazini lika Jesu;
Ngi thol’ ukuxolelwa: Egazini lika Jesu.

Ngi ngavunywa ng’ubani? Ng’uJesu ngegazi lAkhe;
Ngi ngaphete lutho na? Yebo ngal’ igazi lAkhe!

Li miph’ ithemba lami? Egazini lika Jesu;
Kuph’ ukulunga kwami? Egazini lika Jesu.

Ngi babaz’ ubani na? UJesu ngegazi lAkhe;
Ngodums’ ubani na? UJesu ngegazi lAkhe.

Ku mnand’ ukwethemb’ uJesu, Nokukholw’ izwi lAkhe;
Nokubamb’ isithembiso "I sho njalo iNkosi."

Wo! Ku mnandi ukuthemba Ukwethemba igazi;
Ukulazi lelothemba Ku sisa k’uMsindisi.

Ye, ku mnandi ukumthemba Ukushiya izono;
Ukwethemba owalenga Ku senzela uxolo.

Ngi funde ukukwethemba, Jesu, Msindisi wami;
Ngi y’azi u nami Wena, Kuze kube nanini.

hymns.chorus:
Yek’ usuk’ oluhle! A ngi hlamb’ izon’ uJesu;
Wangifundis’ ukulinda;
Ukuhlala ngi thandaza;
Yek’ usuk’ oluhle! A ngi hlamb’ izon’ uJesu.

hymns.lyrics:
Abez, abeNkosi, Abathand’ uMbuso,
Dumisa ngengom’ emnandi;
Dumisa ngengom’ emnandi;
Hloniph’ ubukosi.
Hloniph’ ubukosi.

Ngeke ba hlabele, Abangehloniphe,
Kodw’ abantwana beNkosi;
Kodw’ abantwana beNkosi;
Bo yohlabelela.
Bo yohlabelela.

iNtaba yeZion’, I thel’ okumnandi,
Si ngakafik’ ezulwini;
Si ngakafik’ ezulwini;
S’nyathel’ igolide.
S’nyathel’ igolide.

Zandiswe ingoma, Inyembezi zome,
Dumo ku Emanueli;
Dumo ku Emanueli;
Mholi w’ezulwini.
Mholi, w’ezulwini.

S’ophumula ngas’emanzini, Acwengekileyo;
Khona uJesu u lindile Si yombona lapho.

Nxa si diniwe ukuhamba, Ku mnand’ ukuhlala;
Duze namanzi okuphila, Emthonjen’ omusha.

Ngako k’uJesu Krestu woza, U qiniswe, u me;
Ng’Yen’ amanzi okuphila, Nath’ u ngabusoma.

Nxa uJes’ ebutha izizwe Ukuma ngapambi kwAkhe;
Si zobonakala kanjani: Ukamkel’ ukwahlulelwa.

Kumb’ uMsindisi u yakusho? "Khuhle ncek’ elungileyo;"
Mhlaumbe ngokuthuthumela, Si zoxoshwa ngakuYena.

U yabathabela abAkhe Lab’ abahophau lwAkhe;
U yabagqokisa ngobuhle, Sebe guqile ngakuYe.

Masibe ngabalindileyo Ngeziban’ ezikhanyayo;
Nxa uMyeni esesibiza, Si lungele ukundiza.

Ngenhliziy’ ebhek’ ezulwini Nasekubekezeleni;
Nxa ukuhamba ku phelile, Si zobon’ ubuso bAkhe.

Se si menyelwe eMthimbeni, Sindawonye esithebeni;
Kobanjani kuwe nakimi; iNkos’ i ngena.

Awusek’ umqhele wameva, Ngowobukhosi kuY’ ekhanda;
Yokhazima ekufikeni, iNkos’ i ngena.

Njengombani u khazimula, Into zonke zobasobala;
Lapho soba nak’ ukwazama, iNkos’ i ngena.

Yojabula ukusibona, Igqok’ ezimhlophe zoMthimba;
Kazi si yophumelela na? iNkos’ i ngena.

Si phe Nkosi umusa wAkho, Si size ngesihau sAkho;
Size si ngabi nakwesala, iNkos’ i ngena.

Zwan’ ilizwi loMalusi Le ehlane elimnyama;
Li biz’ izmvu zeNkosi Ezikude nesibaya.

Ng’ubani-ke, ozohamba Ayocinga abaduki;
Ng’ubani ozobalanda Bez lapha ba ngabhubhi.

Zwana ukukhala kwazo Ezintaben’ ezinkulu;
UJes’ uMalusi wakho u thi: "Buyisa izimvu."

Amasimu a lindile, Amhlophe ngamabele;
Ekude si wabonile, Ezigangen’ ezinhle.

Ba thumele ekuseni Nantambama ba ngemi;
Noma se li shon’ ilanga, Mavavun’ izinyanda.

Wen’ othunywayo iNkosi Vunisis’ amabele;
Bhek’ ezulwin’ isiphelo, Wothol’ umvuz’ omkulu.

Qina ku yez’ ukuhlwa; Qin’ imin’ i khona.
Namazol’ a sekhona; Imbal’ i hluma;
Ku se khon’ ukukhanya, Qin’ imin’ i khona;
Qina ku yez’ ukuhlwa, Kophela konke!

Qina ku yez’ ukuhlwa, Li zoshon’ ilanga.
Sebenz’ imini yonke, U nga phumuli;
Yenza ku gcwale konke, Ku nga phuthi lutho;
Qina ku yez’ ukuhlwa, Kophela konke.

Qina ku yez’ ukuhlwa, A yez’ amathunzi.
Laphay’ entshonalanga, se ku ntambama;
Qina sekuzophela, Zama u kuthale;
Ngoba ku yez’ ukuhlwa, Kophela konke.

Ngi babaz’ amandl’ eNkosi A dal’ izintaba;
Nal’ ulwandle alweneka, Nesibhakabhaka;
Ngi babaza leyongqondo, Nelanga yalenza,
Nenyang’ ebus’ ebusuku, Yebo, nenkanyezi!

Ngi babaz’ umusa waYo, O si pha ukudla;
Ya dala ngelizwi laYo, Wonke amabandla;
Si bon’ izimangaliso, Nhlangothini zonke,
Njalo ku yamangalisa, OkweNkosi konke!

Ngi babaza zon’ imbali, Utshani, nenkungu;
Ku yafakaza ngoMenzi, Noba ku thule du!
NgaYe ku yaphila naphi, Ku yondliwa kona.
Si ngabalekela ngaphi?, Nalapho u khona!

Ku mnandi ukukhuleka Ku ngi nqanda osizini;
Ku ngibikela kuBaba Konke ukuswela kwami;
Ngezikhathi zenhlupheko Ngi vama ukupholiswa;
Ngi phunyuk’ ekkulingweni Nges’ khathi sokukhuleka.

Ku mnandi ukukhuleka Ku zothwala izcelo;
KuYe iqiniso lAkhe Li busisa olindayo;
U thi mangi fune Wena Ngi likholwe izwi lAkho,
KuWe ngi zoletha konke Nge linde ngokukhuleka.

Ku mnandi ukukhuleka Ingathi ngi ngaduduzwa;
Ngize ngibone ikhaya Ngi phaphele khona kuYe.
Kuthu ngumzimba omusha; Ngenyuke ngi thol’ umvuzo.
Ngi memeze, Ngi memeze; Sala kahle kukhuleka!

Lindani iNkosi, Iyabiza namhla;
Lindani iNkosi, Lindani ngamandla.
Qinani maKrestu; Isitha si nonya
Lindani uMyeni, Nanxa elibala.

Xosha ubuthongo, susa ukusola.
Ngowakho umvuzo, Phezulu wophumla;
Linda u khuleke, uJesu walinda
Waze wajuluka, Igazi laconsa.

Thembani kuJesu, Qaphelan’ isitha;
Thathan’ izihlangu, Ni lind’ iNkos’ iza;
Uma sekusile Ni ngabolibala;
Ngales’ khath’ esihle, Linda mKrestu linda.

hymns.chorus:
Mlindenini ni khuleke;
Mlindenini ebusuku nasemini;
Lindani nonke.

hymns.lyrics:
Ni ngabokhohlwa iSabatha leNkosi;
Yebo, lihle kunawo wonke amalanga.
Li yasiphumuza emsebenzini yethu;
Li silethel’ ukuphumula kwaphezulu.

Li londoloze iSabatha Mdumise
Owathi Yena, Ngi yindlela yokuphila
Nxa si mlandela uMsindisi wethu lapha
U zosipha amanzi okuphila Yena

Ngelanga eliNgcwele si zakumbonga;
uJesu iSihlobo esithandekayo;
NguMsindisi Yena onothando nomusa;
Izithembiso zAkhe zi ukuthokoza.

Si zwile into enhle, uJes’ uMsindisi;
Ye! u yasisindisa, uJes’ uMsindisi,
Yazais’ izizwe zonke, Ngaphesheya kolwandle;
iNkos’ i yasithuma, NgoJes’ uMsindisi.

Dumisa, dumisani uJes’ uMsindisi;
Zixoxele izoni, NgoJes’ uMsindisi,
Hlabel’ ezinqhingini, Sabela nawe lwandle;
Ngaleyondaba enhle, ke Jes’ uMsindisi.

Hlaba kakhul’ umkhosi, ngoJes’ uMsindisi;
Nokufa nangempilo, ka Jes’ uMsindisi,
Wusho nasemnyameni, Nxa wondel’ isihawu;
Wolinqoba ithuna, NgoJes’ uMsindisi.

Phonsa emoyen’ izwi, NgoJes’ uMsindisi;
Thabani nonke zizwe, NgoJes’ uMsindisi,
Memeza usindiso, ebintabeni zonke;
Ingoma yokunqoba, Ka Jes’ uMsindisi.

Ngi zwe, Nkosi, ubenomsa kimi Za Mkhululi woza;
uMoya wami u fisa Wena Za Mkhululi Woza.

Asikho isiphephelo sami Za Mkhululi;
Ngi bheke ngi thole ukukhanya Za Mkhululi Woza.

Indlela yam’ i yangikhataza Za Mkhululi, Woza;
Amehlo’ ami a bheke uthando Za Mkhululi, Woza.

U ngalahl’ ukuzisola kwami Za Mkhululi, Woza;
Lalela ukukhuleka kwami Za Mkhululi, Woza.

Memezela ngamandl’ okukhulula Ukukhulula abahloniphayo;
Emlilweni wokulahlwa kwezoni uJesu u zokhulula ozayo.

A ngakhulula u qinisile na? A khona amandla a ngangisiza?
Ngi tshele u Krestu owabethelwa A ngangikhulula kuSathani na?

A ngakhulula! Mana isibindi U ngesabi, bambelela kuJesu;
U ngesabi, bambelela kuJesu Khaul’ ukungabaza, yimi kuYe

Ku khon’ ilang’ entabeni, Ku khon’ ilang’ olwandle,
Ukukhanya ku yahlala, Emangweni omuhle.
Ukukhanya ku gcwalisa Umxhwele wenhliziyo;
U lapho, Wena Msindisi Nangokukhanya kwAkho.

Ngi lahla usizi lwami Njengengubo endala;
U ngembese ngokuthaba Wangipha ukubonga.
Le ekhaya lobukhosi, Owang’ zuzela lona;
Inhliziyo iyavuma, Nawo umoya wami.

uMsindisi wangithenga Se ngi ngo wAkhe mina.
Ma si khanye isibane Si khanyele iNkosi;
Le ekhaya lobukhosi Owang’ zuzela lona;
Inhliziyo iyavuma, Nawo umoya wami.

Ngi ngowAkho, Nkosi ngi zwil’ izwi, Langitshela ngothando;
Ngi fis’ ukuqin’ ekukholweni, Ngi donselwe eduze.

Ngi zinikela ngokusha kuWe, Ngamandla amakhulu;
Umoya wami u qonda kuWe, U fihleke kuJesu.

O! ukubamnandi kwesikhathi, Ngi phambili kwes’hlalo
Nxa ngiguqa ngi khuleka, Nkosi, Ngi khuluma noMhlobo.

Ku nothando olungaqondwayo, Ngi ngakayi phesheya;
Ku nokuthokoz’ engingakwazi Ngi ngakafiki khona.

Eduze nes’phambano, Ku noMthomb’ omuhle;
Amanzi okwelapha, Evela kuJesu.

Eduze nes’phambano, Umsa wangithola;
Lapho ngakhanyiselwa, Intando ka Jesu.

Eduze nes’phambano, Ngi hlale neWundlu;
Ngi size ‘nsuku zonke, Ngi landel’ ithunzi.

Eduze nes’phambano, Ngothemba ngi linde;
Ukuze ngi yofika, Phesheya komfula.

O! vuma ngi hambe, Nkosi: NjengoEnok’ wayehamba;
Ngi thathe ngesandla sAkho U khulume mnandi nami;
Noma ngi ngabon’ indlela Kodwa ngi zohamba naWe.

Anginako ukuhamba, Kudum’ izulu, nes’phepho.
Uhlupho lu yangithiya, Izitha zi yangilinga;
Kuzo lezi ‘zinhlupheko: ‘Nkosi, vuma ng’hambe naWe.

Nxa u thath’ isandla sami, Ngi zohamba ngokwethaba.
Ngesibindi endleleni, Ngi zothwal’ isisphambano;
Ngize ngi bon’ amasango; O! ‘Nkosi, mang’ hambe naWe.

uJesu nguMholi wami, Wo ngi hola yonk’ indlela;
Ng’ uMholi wami impela Ngi khumbula eKhalvari.

Ngi thand’ umthetho ka Jesu Ngi holwa yisandla sAkhe;
I mnand’ intando yAkhe kim’ I cwebiswe yi Khalvari.

Ngi ya phambili nges’bindi uKrest’ u seduze kwami;
Ngi themb’ uJesu ngombona, Isihlobo seKhalvari.

Thath’ izwe u ngiph’ uJesu Ubuhle balo yize;
Uthando lweNkosi lumi, Yilo njalo phakade.

Thath’ izwe u ngiph’ uJesu Isiduduzo sami;
Ngalusiwe nguMsindisi Ngi yohuba kukubi.

Thath’ izwe u ngiph’ uJesu Ngi mbon’ emomotheka;
Khuthi ohambweni lwami Ngi qinise kukhanya.

Thath’ izwe u ngiph’ uJesu Ng’thembel’ es’phambanweni;
Ngize ngi bone obala Si bhekana noJesu.

Se ngi fumene uMhlobo, Wang’ thanda ngi ngamazi;
Ngadonswa ngalo uthando, Nje wangibopha kuYe;
Kuyo inhliziyo yami: Les’bopho si qinile.
Jesu, ngi ngowAkho mina Kuze kube nanini.

Se ngi fumene uMhlobo, Wopha wangisindisa;
Kungasikuphila kodwa, Kepha waz’dela Yena.
Konke enginako mina Ngi kuphathel’ uMniki;
Inhliziyo nenhlalo yam’ OkwAkhe naphakade.

Se ngi fumene uMhlobo, Onk’ amandla waphiwa;
Uma engelinda mina Ngendlela yaphezulu;
Ku yakhanya udumo le: Olungiqinisayo;
A ngi linde ngi sebenze Phambilii ngophumula.

Se ngi fumene uMhlobo, Onomusa nothando;
U yongiqondisa mina Ngi yofik’ ezulwini;
Ku wena ongithandayo Ngi yawathol’ amandla
Si ngahlukaniswa ‘kufa! Qha ngi ngowAkho mina

Ngi fisa ukuba ngowAkho, O Msindisi wami;
Ngi fundise intando yAkho, Ngi size, Nkosi.

Imfuyo yomhlaba i yini, Nkosi nxa u ngekho;
Ngi yakudela konke mina Ngi zuz’ okwAkho.

Ngi lahla okomhlaba konke Buy’ eduze, Nkosi;
KuWe nganele ngako konke Msindisi wami.

Yek’ ubumnandi bosuku!
Luhle kuzo zonke;
Si lahl’ im’camango yezwe;
Si camang’izulu.

O! mahl’ amazw’ okuthula,
Kowamukelayo;
A nosizi lwenguquko;
Esisa ekhaya.

Nanxa si xosha ukona;
Amandla engekho,
Lo obona inhliziyo;
Yena wosisiza.

Nkosi busis’ ukuphuma;
Thabis’ umoya wethu:
Si phe sonk’ uthando lwAkho;
Ngomusa si yonqoba
Si ph’ amandla, u sivuse;
Nxa si hamba ehlane!

Si kubonga, si dumisa;
Ngelizwi leVangeli.
Izithelo zosindiso;
Zi bonakale kithi.
Si kholele, njalo, njalo;
Si neqiniso lAkho.

Nxa insuku zethu zanda;
‘Ngathi kunga ezAkho.
Si kuthale mihla yonke;
Si gijime, si ngemi;
Si ncome udumo lwAkho,
Izulu li vuleke.

Ungazenz’ izaba, ku khon’ umsebenzi, Lungela ukwenza iNkos’ ekushoyo;
Ukunxusa kwaYo, ku qondiswe kuwe, Yamkel’ uze wenze umsebenzi waYo.

Ungazenz’ izaba, namhla u yabizwa; Kade u ngavumi, pangis’ u lalele;
Ku vuthw’ amasimu, akukho muvumi, Ma u thobe wena, wenzele iNkosi.

Ungazenz’ izaba, balekel’ ingozi, Ncuthando loniwe, lu muka phakade;
Uma u sancengwa, u tshelwa ngezulu, UJes’ esancenga: "Woz’ u thethelelwe!"

Baba ngi sondeze eduze Ngifun’ u ngi gone.
Ngi singath’ engalweni zAkho Ngi fun’ ukuphumla.

Msindisi ngi sondeze kuWe Ngi ngadedi kuWe;
Ngothab’ ezingalweni zAkho, Ngithi se kwanele.

Ngi sondeze ngoMoya wAkho Ngi fanane naWe;
Ng’vuse, ng’lungise, ngi hlanzeke; Ngi ze ngi bemsulwa.

Nakuphi noJesu ngi ngahamba nje Noma ku kuphi kulomhlaba wonke;Ngaphandle kwAkhe a ngi nakuthaba Laph’ uJesu ekhona a ngesabi.

Nxa ngi kuphi noJesu a ngi ngedwa Nxa ngi delwa ngabany’ u khona Yena;
Noma ezongiholela ehlane, Nxa uJesu ekhona ku lungile.

Nxa ngi kuphi noJesu ngi ngalala Nxa ithunzi lokufa li sondela;
Noko ngi yobuya ngi vuke mina Ngi y’ezulwini ekhaya kuJesu.

Msindisi, nje ngomalusi, Si hole ngomsa wAkho,
Ehlungwini lAkho sondle; U sakhele is’baya,
Jes ‘oweth’ obusisiwe! Was’ thenga si ngabAkho;
Jes ‘oweth’ obusisiwe! Was’ thenga si ngabAkho.

Si ngabAkh’ u bosilinda, Mqondisi wezindlela;
Si vikele esonweni, Si bone si ngaduki.
Jes ‘oweth’ obusisiwe! Yizwa O, Nkosi yethu,
Jes ‘oweth’ obusisiwe! Yizwa O, Nkosi yethu.

Wathembis’ ukusithola, Thina zoni nxa si nje;
U nomusa wokusipha Si gezwe si bemhlophe;
Jes ‘oweth’ obusisiwe! Si zobuyela kuWe,
Jes ‘oweth’ obusisiwe! Si zobuyela kuWe.

Ezwen’ elingashazwa: Emzin’ okhanyayo;
Awusoze wa guga, Ubusuk’ abukho.

Amasang’ aligugu; Emzin’ okhanyayo;
Im’gwaqo yigolide, Ubusuk’ abukho.

Amasang’ angevalwe: Emzin’ okhanyayo;
Nempilo a yipheli, Ubusuk’ abukho.

Ka ba dingi nenyanga: Emzin’ okhanyayo;
IWundlu li yilanga, Ubusuk’ abukho.

Is’khathi a saziwa sona, Ayobuya ngaso lapha;
Kumbe kuyakuba ‘ntambama, Kumb’ ebusuku impela:
Kumb’ ekuthatheni kokusa, Mani qaphele, ni lunge;
Zi ngabocima izibani, Ma si mlinde, si mqaphele.

Ngomsa wAkhe ngi yakhumbula, Intengo a s’thenge ngaYo.
Wa shiy’ izindlu zobukhosi, Weza lapha emhlabeni;
Ngi yazi kuhle eNkosini, Uma thina esifele,
Izosifumanisa sonke Si lindele, si qaphele.

O! Jesu Wena, Mhlengi wami, U yalaz’ ithemba lami;
Eliyakubona ngamehlo, Nxa se ngi kuzw’ u ‘thi, Woza.
Abanye, bona ba ngesaba Nxa u qhamuka, Mahluli,
Qa, mina ngi thol’ isihlobo Ngi zolinda, ngi qaphele.

Ngi ngomkhulu umoni, uJesu wangifela,
Waf’ ukuba ngi phile, Waf’ ukuba ngi ngafi.
Njengegatsh’ evinini, Se ngi ngoWakhe nami.

Lud’ uthando lweNkosi, Phezulu, lu phakeme;
Lu yadlula ulwandle, Lu yahlala anini;
Lwangizuza ngi sona, Ngangingamdingi Yena

Nakhona ngi ng’umoni, Ukrestu yiko konke;
Ukwazi kahle konke, Ukuhlupheka kwami;
Ngi zophephela kuYe, Emhlabeni ozayo

Esiphambanweni laphaya, uMsindisi wachith’ igazi
Nami khona ngagezisiswa Dumisa Yena

Si khulu sona isimanga! Ngi sindisiwe ezonweni;
Ku mnand’ uJes’ u hlala nami Dumisa Yena.

Emthonjen’ ophilis’ izoni Ngi thabile se ngi ngenile;
uJesu u se ngi hlambile Dumisa Yena.

Woza kuloMthombo omnandi, Khuwo u ziphonse namhlanje;
U hlanjisiwe, u phelele Dumisa Yena

U fis’ ukwethulwa isono na? A khon’ amandla egazini;
U fis’ ukunqoba okubi na? A khon’ amandl’ egazini.

U fis’ ukudela ulaka na? A khon’ amandla egazini;
Woza u zohlanzwa kulo wena A khon’ amandl’ egazini.

U yafisa ukuba mhlophe qhwa! A khon’ amandla egazini;
Woza u zohlanzwa kulo wena A khon’ amandl’ egazini.

U ngesebenzele iNkosi na? A khon’ amandla egazini;
U fisa ukuyidumisa na? A khon’ amandl’ egazini.

Akukh’ okositha nx’ uJes’ eza;
Akukh’ okositha nx’ uJes’ eza;
Akukh’ okositha nx’ uJes’ eza;
Nxa ezothath’ abAkhe.

Kungebekho ‘nsizi nxa’ uJes’ eza;
Kungebekho ‘nsizi nxa’ uJes’ eza;
Kungebekho ‘nsizi nxa’ uJes’ eza;
Nxa ezo thath’ abAkhe.

Akuy’ ukulilwa nx’ uJes’ eza;
Akuy’ ukulilwa nx’ uJes’ eza;
Akuy’ ukulilwa nx’ uJes’ eza;
Nxa ezo thath’ abAkhe.

Kohlatshelwa mnandi nx’ uJes’ eza;
Kohlatshelwa mnandi nx’ uJes’ eza;
Kohlatshelwa mnandi nx’ uJes’ eza;
Nxa ezo thath’ abAkhe.

Makubongw’ iNkosi ngekwenzileyo,
Yathand’ ilizwe yasiph’ uJesu;
Wadel’ ukuphila ngezono zethu,
Wavula isango si ngene ngalo.

Yek’ inkululo ithengwe ngegazi!
Sithembiso seNkosi kokholwayo;
Isoni esibi esikholwayo
Masinya si yaxolelwa nguJesu.

Kukhul’ akwenzile wakufundisa;
Inkul’ intokozo ngay’ iNdodana,
Koba kuhle kuphakame, kumsulwa;
Lapho si bona senyuka noJesu.

Ngi yamuzwa uMsindisi Engibiza ngoMlandela;
Endlebeni ath’ amazwi Nsuku zonke, ungilandele.

Noma indlela imnyama Nezinyawo zi khathele,
Inhliziyo iyakhanya Nxa ngi Mlandela yonk’indlela.

UJesu engendulele Izulu li yakhazimla,
Ngi nikwe amandl’ amanye Nxa ngi Mlandela yonk’ indlela

Ngi hole esigodini U ngi phakele ukudla;
Nkosi, nginced’ ebubini Nxa ngi landela yonk’ indlela.

Z’u ngi thwale ngenhliziyo U nami owAkho umsa;
Z’u ngi gone ngezingalo Nxa ngi landela yonk’ indlela

UMsindisi wangophela, Yaf’ iNkosi yami;
Wazidela, wangifela, Ngi sindiswe nami.

Ngenxa yem’sebenzi yami, Yek’ uthando lomsa! 
Walenga Yena emthini, Ku yamangalisa!

Usizi kaluhlawuli Elami icala;
’Nkosi, nguWe inhlawulo ‘Ngi yazinikela!

Njengemv’ ezul’entabeni Iduke nezinye;
Ngi ngathol’ indlela njani Ebuyel’ ekhaya?

Insizi zingididile Sengi fun’iNkosi;
Abanye bathi, Lenale! Iqiniso liphi?

Krest’ ukuPhila neNdlela Ngi ngeze ngamshiya;
Wongiqondisa kuBaba Ngi hlale ekhaya.

Sukumelan’ uJesu Mabuth’ es’phambano;
Misan’ umthetho wAkhe Mani ngawu lahli,
Ninqobe nokunqoba Imp’ iholwa nguYe;
Size sichithw’ isitha uJesu abuse.

Sukumelan’ uJesu Lalelani izwi;
Yiyanini empini Ngal’usuk’ oluhle,
Madoda, mukhonzeni Phakathi kwezitha;
Niqine engozini Lwanini ngamandla.

Sukumelan’ uJesu Thembelani kuYe;
Nowa nxa nizethemba Ningazisho neze!
Hlomani ngeVangeli Nikhuleke njalo;
Nxa nibizwa kukubi Ningaphuthi lapho.

Sukumelan’ uJesu Impi izophela;
Namhla kunga dum’ impi Ngomso ukunqoba,
Nobani onqobayo Wothweswa umqhele;
Yena kanye noJesu Wobusa phakade.

Ngoban’ abadlul’ amagagasi, Phesheya kwama ngcwaba bathi, thu!NgoJesu bedumisa, Behlanziwe liWundlu.

Yibo labo ebusheni babo Bahlakani pha ba kheth’ uJesu;
Benela ngaYe labo Behlanziwe liWundlu

Yibo abathwal’ inhlungu laba Bazuza ukuphumla k’uJesu;
Begcwele ukuthula Behlanziwe liWundlu

Yibo abaphathekayo kabi Bema emlilweni obuhlungu
UJes’ uthi, "Nyukani!" Nihlanziwe liWundlu.

Baphephel’ ogwin’ olukhanyayo Sekudlule ukufa nenhlungu;
Bathaba njalo-njalo Behlanziwe liWundlu.

hymns.chorus:
Ilizwe laseKhenani Ngiya kuma eNtabeni,
Ngithalaze ngaphesheya lapho kun’elam’ ikhaya;
Ngiya bona lon’ izulu, Isigodlo sakoMkhulu

hymns.lyrics:
Intamb’ ebophela, Inhliziyo zethu;
Kulo uthando lwezulu, Sibusiso sethu.

Phambili kwes’hlalo, Sizo zincengela;
Ukwesaba nokulila, Kwethu ku yophela.

Inhlupheko zethu, Nayo imithwalo;
Noku khalelana kwethu, Konke ku ndawonye

Nxase sehlukana, Kubanga usizi;
Kodwa siyethemba sizo, Hlangana phambili.

Vuka moya vuka! Thintit’ ukwesala.
Umhlatshel’ ob’hlungu, Uvezelwe mina.
Es’hlalwen’ uJes’ ung’mele;
Es’hlalwen’ uJes’ ung’mele;
Ngilotshiw’ esandlen’ sAkhe.

Uhlel’ ezulwini, Ukunginxusela.
Ngothand’ ol’hlengayo, Negaz’ el’ncengayo.
Igazi lAkhe las’thenga;
Igazi lAkhe las’thenga;
Lifafaz’ is’hlalo somsa.

Mahlan’ amanxeba, Ahlatshw’ eKhalvari.
Ahlal’ ekhuleka, Ayang’ khulumela.
Athi mxolele, mxolele;
Athi mxolele, mxolele;
Angafi ophendukayo.

Uyis’umzw’ encenga Ogcotshiwe wAkhe.
Angefulathele iNdodana yAkhe.
NoMoya uyamuzwela;
NoMoya uyamuzwela;
Uthi, ngizelwe yiNkosi.

‘Za kuJesu, ‘Za kuJesu, ‘Za kuJesu manje;
Manje, Wena kuYe, Woza kuYe manje.

Wosindiswa, Wosindiswa, Wosindiswa manje;
Manje, Wosindiswa, Woza kuYe manje.

Unamandla, Unamandla, Unamandla, manje;
Manje, Unamandla, Woza kuYe manje.

Cela kuYe, Cela kuYe, Cela kuYe, manje;
Manje, Ulindele, Woza kuYe manje.

Ulindele, Ulindele, Ulindele manje;
Manje, Ulindele, Woza kuYe manje.

Themba kuYe, Themba kuYe, Themba kuYe, manje;
Manje, Themba kuYe, Woza kuYe, manje.

Wobusiswa, Wobusiswa,Wobusiswa manje;
Manje, Wobusiswa, Woza kuYe manje.

Sine bizo likaJesu Elithandeka kithi;
Phezulu bathemba lona Nathi sithemba lona.

Alikho ibizw’ elihle Elithob’ inhliziyo;
Ngaphandle kwelika Jesu Nom’ enamil’ umuntu.

Ngiyathemba ngizombona, Nxa ezothath’ abAkhe.
Ngiyathemba ngizombona Ngithabe emoyeni.

Nxa evuma Ngisebenze Ensimini yeNkosi;
Kuhle kuphela uJesu Abusise okwami.

Nxa evuma nima ngife, Kuhle ngifele kuYe;
Kuhle kuphela uJesu Abe lithemba lami.

Phons’ izwana ngoJesu-uMhlobo impela.
Vus’ inhliziyo zethu, Ngekwenzele kona.

Phons’ izwana ngoJesu-Lok’us’xolelwe.
Zama ngowAkhe umsa Ufik’ ekhaya le!

Phons’ izwana ngoJesu-Njalo wena usho;
Ngiyamthand’ uMsindisi, Owangifelayo.

Phons’ izwana ngoJesu-Kusekhon’ ithuba;
Ngokuthula uthi, du! Uyavuna ombi.

Phons’ izwana ngoJesu-Ithemba nxa lifa;
Sukuma kubunhlungu Umethembe Yena.

hymns.chorus:
Zanini kiMi, en’si ndwayo;
Nin’ abakhathele nginganiphumuza;
Thwalan’ ijoka nifunde ngaMi;
Ngi munene Ngithobiles nothi; Nithol’ ukuphumula

hymns.lyrics:
Kwavel’ inkanyez’ ebusuku, Yakhanyiswa nguNkulunkulu
Im’sebe yahola izazi; Zaqondiswa kuMsindisi

Zazi ngeM’bhalo iqiniso, Lenkanyezi ekhanyisayo;
Zalindel’ uk’khanya khashana, Oku nguKrestu indonsa

Solandel’ uk’khanya kwendulo, Loko kukhanya okwashiwo;
Solandela siy’ ezulwini, Sifike ‘kuphumuleni

hymns.chorus:
Zibethelw’ emthini, Zibethelw’ emthini;
Wezwa ‘buhlung’ obukhulu
U Jesu emthini wakhala ngomunyu Ethwel’ izono zami lapho

Uyanaka Ngi yamazi U yangidabukela;
Nxa ngiphel’ amandla
Nxa ngingalali, Uyang’ nak’ uJesu

hymns.lyrics:
Mlindi, vuthel’ ixilongo, Banike isiyalo;
Lowo uvayo indaba, Angaguquk’ aphile.

Likhalise entabeni, Kuyo yonke indawo;
Base lwandle mememzani, Indaba yokuphila.

Limemeze endleleni, Endaweni emnyama;
Nitsho "Zinto zilungile, uBaw’ usilindile."

Xelela abasindwayo, Abanwenel’ uYesu;
Isimemo so-Msindisi Sithi, "Yizani kumi."

i-Nkosi seyisemnyango, Eyathwala umnqamlezo;
Ngoku abalungileyo, Baya phila ngayo.

Into zonke zibonisa, ’kuza kwayo kusondele;
Siza kubona kamsinya, Ukuza kokusa.

Ninga khangel’ emhlabeni, Inkathazo azipheli;
Kuza kufik’ uMsindisi, Abhangis’ ukufa.

Khona ezweni elitsha, Sosoloko singabatsha;
Apho kungekho nkathazo, Kude kube nini.

hymns.chorus:
Emnyango . . . emnyango. . . i-Nkosi ifikil’ emnyango;
Iyeza, iyeza, Seyifikil’ emnyango.
(Iyeza iNkosi, Iyeza iNkosi; Seyifikil’ emnyango)

hymns.lyrics:
Ukubonana ngobuso No-Kristu uMsindisi;
Loba njanina uvuyo, Lokumbona uYesu!

Ngok’ ndibona kaluzizi, kuko okusithayo;
Liyez’ ilanga elihle, ndobon’ uzuko lwaKhe.

Ndiya kugcob’ ukumbona, Kophela ukukhala;
Konke okungaziwayo kwa kukhanyiswa khona.

Ukubonana ngobuso Naye uMphathi wami;
Siya kubukana thina noYesu uMsindisi.

Zimnand’ indab’ endlebeni yesihambi, Xa sizula kude nekhaya,
Kukufuphi ukubuya koMsindisi, nombuso uya buya.

Aba kade belele emangcwabeni Baza kuvuka ekufeni;
Kwa nabo base lwandle olunamandla, Baseza kufuman’ impilo.

Sakuhlangana elizweni elitsha Ngengoma yabakhululweyo;
Abavela kude kumazwe aseNtla Sikhonze iNkosi yezulu.

Haleluya amen!  Haleluya amen! Kamsinyane siya kufika;
Themba uphakamise intloko yaKho, Iyez’ iNkosi nesitsaba.

Lindani, niphaphamile, Bonani iziboniso;
Khanyisani izibane, Ngoba uYesu uyeza.

Isithembiso seNkosi, Isisa esathengwayo;
’Zambatho ezinegazi Zixela imbali yaso.

Zilawuli zichithekile, Yiv’ amasond’ edilika;
Xelan’ isisa sandile,  Ixilongo lisakhala.

Izizwe ziyaxabana, Mbuso kaThix’ usondele;
Umhlaba lo uyankwantya, ixesha seliphelile.

Boni yizani ku-Yesu, Usanimel’ ezulwini;
Ngxaman’ inceb’ iyaphela, U-Yes’ uyeza kamsinya.

Likhaliseni ixilongo bo!  ’Yes’ uyaphind’ ukuza;
Qinisa mhambi, memelelani, ’Yes’ uyaphind’ ukuza.

Hlokomisani ezintabeni, ’Yes’ uyaphind’ ukuza;
I-Mvana seyikufuphi namhla, ’Yes’ uyaphind’ ukuza.

Khwazan’ zilwandle, Phezu kwamaza, ’Yes’ uyaphind’ ukuza;
Elunxwemeni, mabeve bonke, ’Yes’ uyaphind’ ukuza.

Iziboniso zisixelela, ’Yes’ uyaphind’ ukuza;
Umoya uyaduma kakhulu, ’Yes’ uyaphind’ ukuza.

Izizwe ziyabonisa mpela, ’Yes’ uyaphind’ ukuza;
Abantu bonke mabaqondise, ’Yes’ uyaphind’ ukuza.

Sohlangana emlanjeni, Apho kukhanya kuhle;
Amanzi emahle lawo, avela ku-Yehova.

Elunxwemeni lomlambo, sohamba sibulisa;
Sidumis’ uThixo wethu, Imihla yonke khona.

Emlanjeni wokukhanya, sowulahla umthwalo;
Ngesisa saku khululwa, samkele izitsaba.

Emlanjeni okhanyayo, usizi alukho tu
Intliziyo zakuvuya, Ngobuhle obukhulu.

Ndokulandela msindisi, Ngawo onke amaxa;
Xa ukhoyo ndolandela, Ewe, ndokulandela.

Nox’ indlela inameva, Igqunywe emanzini;
Leyo ndlela wayihamba, Ngako ndokulandela.

Nakuzo ezi nkathazo Ndilingeka kanzima;
Nkos’ uyayazi nendlela, Ngako ndokulandela.

Naxa ndiv’ ukhathazeko, ndinguy’ odeliweyo;
wena wahlungiswayo nje, Ngako ndokulandela.

Naxa umlambo uzele, Ndowuwela ndinaWe;
Wena wahamba elwandle, Ngako ndokulandela.

Kukho umthombo wegazi, Ovel’ eNkosini;
’Boni, abahlanjiweyo Kulo elo gazi,
Bayahlanjululwa Ezonweni zabo.
’Boni abahlanjiweyo Bayahlanjululwa.

Isela elajingayo Lavuy’ ukubona
Lowo mthombo wokuphila, Ohlamba izono
Noxa ndinezono Ndingahlanjululwa;
Lowo mthombo wokuphila, Ohlama izono.

Wena Mvana eyafayo, Sesibonga wena;
I-Bandla lingasindiswa NguWe ezonweni;
Linamandl’ igazi Ukuhlamb’ izono;
I-Bandla lingasindiswa NguWe ezonweni.

Ngokholo ndabon’ umsinga Ovel’ enxebenii;
Ndathabatheka luthando, ndahlanjwa izono.
Ndohlala ndivuma ngaWe Ndide ndikubone.
Ndathabatheka luthando, ndahlanjwa izono.

Nkosi undilungisele Indawo ekhaya;
Noxa ndingakufanele, Wena wandifela;
Undiphil’ umvuzo Kuyimpila entsha;
Noxa ndingakufanele, Wena wandifela.

Ndinengoma yokuvuma Ngosindiso lwaKho;
Xa ndimbona uMsindisi Ndiyakumdumisa.
Lo mzimba woba ngomnye, Sowenziwe wamtsha,
Xa ndimbona uMsindisi Ndiyakumdumisa.

Ndizihlambil’ izindla, Hi nje! Zaba mhlophe
Ndizibolek’ uYesu, Ukumsebenzela.

Zindlebe phulaphula Ngayo yonk’ imihla;
Siqondeni isisa Kuzo zonk’ izenzo.

Makalind’ amehlo am Wonke umsebenzi;
Kungabikho okubi, Ngenxa ka-Yesu wam.

Siyavuya ngothando, Luyasonwabisa;
Lusenza sinyamekele Abanye abantu.

Apha kuko usizi, Izono nokufa;
Ngokuvuya sakuzama Ukuzuza omnye.

Bakuphela obubom, Afike u-Yesu,
Soyihlabela ingoma Yothand’ olukhulu.

hymns.chorus:
U-Thix’ uthand’ abancinane, Sifun’ ukufana naYe.
Siyavuya ngothando, Luyasonwabisa;
Lusenza sinyamekele Abanye abantu.

hymns.lyrics:
Ndiza emnqamlezweni, Ndiza ze ndiyimfama;
Konke kuyilahleko, Kuwe kulusindiso.

Iyakhal’ intliziyo, Kade ububi bukum;
U-Yesu thetha nam, "Ndakukuhlambulula."

Ndikunika konk’ okwam, Izihlobo nendyebo,
Umphefumlo nomzimba, Zonke ngonaphakade.

Ndithemb’ idinga laKho, Mandive undihlamba;
Ndiyazithoba kuWe, Ndibethelelwe naWe.

Kunje uYes’ uyeza; Ndofezekiswa kuYe;
Ndibe ngophilileyo; Uzuko lolweMvana.

Ndizalise O Mkhululi, Ngo-Moya Oyingcwele;
Ungumhlobo wethu, Mfeli, Yiza, ngena uhlale.

Ungandizalisa wena - Akungexelelwe ndim;
Ufuneka kakhulu kum, Ngothando ndizalise.

Ndizele bubuthathaka; Ndiguqa engyaweni;
Wena unawo amandla, Ndisize ndiyatshona.

Thuthuzela undihlambe. Ndihlambe intliziyo;
Mthuthuzeli, ndisindise, Wen’ undizalisayo.

Ndiyakufuna kum, Wena Nkosi,
Alikho ilizwi ’LinjengelaKho.

Ndiyakufuna kum, Nceda hlala nam,
Andisokuhluthwa Xa ndinaWe.

Ndiyakufuna kum, Yiza ndisize;
Yiza kamsinyane Undicede

Ndiyakufuna kum, Yiz’ ufundise;
Ngamadinga aKho, ndibabale.

Ndiyakufuna kum, Uyingcwele;
Mandibe ngowaKho, Ndisindise

Konke Yesu ndinikela,  Ndinikela ngesisa;
Ndithembela njalo kuwe, Ndiphile nawe apha.

Konke Yesu ndinikela, Ndiguq’ ezinyaweni
’Nzuzo yomhlaba ndadela, Thatha Yesu, ndithathe.

Konke Yesu ndinikela Ndenze ngcwele, Msindisi;
Ndiphe owaKho u-Moya, Wen’ Ungowam ’ngenene.

Konke Yesu ndinikela, Ndiv’ umlilo ongcwele;
Nal’ uvuyo losindiso, Lube kuye uzuko.

Ndinje, Nkosi, ndiza ndinje, Nali lodwa ilizwi lam,
Lokuba wandifela nam;  Mvana kaThixo, ndiyeza.

Ndinje, Nkosi, ndiza ndinje, Ndinge lisul’ ityala lam;
Ndohlanjwa ngelo gazi nam; Mvana kaThixo, ndiyeza.

Ndinje, Nkosi, ndiza ndinje, Ndinoval’ entliziyweni;
Luphehla umbilini wam, Mvana ka-Thixo, ndiyeza.

Ndinje, Nkosi, Ndiza ndinje, Ndibomvu, ndinobumfama;
Phofu konke usinika, Mvana ka-Thixo, ndiyeza.

Ndinje, Nkosi, ndiza ndinje, Yihlambe intliziyo yam.
Ndicokise, ndihlambise, Mvana ka-Thixo, ndiyeza.

Ndinje, Nkosi, ndiza ndinje, Ndibanga uthando lwaKho;
Ndiyaziphosa, ndingowaKho, Mvana ka-Thixo, ndiyeza.

Thabatha ixesha ukuba ngcwele,
Soloko ukuye ngelizwi laKhe;
Yiba nobuhlobo, siz’ imilwelwe,
Ungazilibali intsikelelo.

Thabatha ixesha emsebenzini,
Zenzele ixesha no-Yesu yedwa;
Khangela ku-Yesu wofana naYe,
Izihlobo zaKho zombona kuwe.

Thabatha ixesha wokukhokela,
Landel’ emva kwaKhe noba kuhlani;
Ekuvuyisweni nasentsizini,
Zingisa ku-Yesu themb’ izwi laKhe.

Thabatha ixesha, Zol’ umphefumlo;
Zonke iingcamango Zilaulwe nguYe;
Wokukhokelela kumthomb’ wothando;
Kwangokumsinyane, Woba phezulu.

Hlala nam kuyeza ukuhlwa; Sekuyahlwa uze uhlale nam;
Apho abanye sebesoyiswa, Wena ungoyiswayo, hlala nam.

Kuyakhawuleza okukufa kwam, Ubuhle obomhlaba buphina?
Izinto zonke zitshabalala, Wen’ ongaguqukiyo hlala nam.

Ndiyakucela yiz’ uhlale nam;  Ungekho, zondoyis’ izilingo;
Ungezi, Nkosi, njengodlulayo, Kodwa, Nkosi yam nced’ uhlale.

Kufunek’ usolok’ uhleli nam, Umlingi uyoyiswa lufefe;
Ngubani ongaz’ abe njengawe? Ngamazolo onke solok’ unam.

Andoyiki xa ndihleli nawe, Inyemvezi azinaburara;
Kufa nencwaba ningenzani kum? Ndinoloyiso xa uhleli nam.

I-Nkos’ ili-Liwa lethu, Isisiphephelo sethu;
Inqaba nomthunzi wethu, Isisiphephelo sethu.

U-Yesu ngumthunzi wethu, Usisiphephelo sethu;
Asoyiki, ungowethu, Usisiphephelo sethu.

Onogumbe bangantlitha, usisiphephelo sethu;
U-Thixo ukukunqaba, Usisiphephelo sethu.

Liwa lethu, Nqaba yethu, Usisiphephelo sethu;
Yiba usolok’ unathi; Usisiphephelo sethu.

U-Yes’ uya ndikhokela, Ngeyakhe intuthuzelo;
Noko konk’ endikwenzayo Isandla sakhe sikho kum.

Noba kumnyama kuthe thsu, Nasemanzin’ enkathazo;
Andinanto ithusayo, Kuba ungaphambili kwam.

Andisoli, andikhali, Nkosi ndiya qinisela;
Kuko konke ndiya vuya, Ekuben’ undikhokela.

Wakuphela umsebenzi, NgaWe Yesu ndingoyisa;
Andikoyika ukufa, U-Yesu endikhokela.

Hai ubudlelane buka-Yesu, O sayamis’ ezingalweni;
Intsikelelo zona zinkulu Xa ndayame kuy’ engalweni.

O, kumnandi ukuba ngumhambi, Ndayam’ engalweni yaKhe;
Indlela iya khanya kumhambi Xa ase zingalweni zaKhe.

Ndingoyika-na? Ndingoyika-ni? Sendinokuthuthuzeleka;
Naxa ndibanjiswe ekulingweni, Ndayama engalweni yaKhe.

Qinisisa ku-Thixo ezweni, Naphakathi kwesiphithiphithi;
Kuphela kwe-Liw’ elinamandla Ekulweni nesono.

Qinisela ukulunga nyulu, Ngentliziyo engoyiki lutho;
Li-Dwala kuphel’ eloyisayo izono zonke apha.

Qinisela i-Nyaniso yonke, Kokulungela ke oko konke;
Li-Dwala kuphel’ elinoxolo Zakudlul’ ezalapha.

Ngu-Yesu oli-Liwa lam, Inguye u-Sindiso lwam;
Ndingeze ndikuthemb’ okwam, Ngu-yesu nje umxhasi wam.

Nobumnyama buphambi kwam, Mandingozeli Nkosi yam;
Nezulu lindiwela nam, Mandinga lahl’ ukholo lwam.

Isifungo siqinile Kubo abamthembileyo;
Xa ithemba seliwile, u-Yesu ndisamthembile.

Xa likhala ixilongo, Ke yena wobonakala,
Eno bungcwalisa bonke, Yena ulilo i-Liwa.

Xa sihlangana nezihlobo Kukho ukuvuya;
Kusinik’ usizi kakhulu Xa se zizakumka.

Siya kuvuya xa sibona Abakuthi apha;
Koko sisa khalela lona Izwe lokuvuya.

Amazwi athi "Sala kuhle" Akathethwa khona;
Koko ingoma ezingcwele Ziya vunywa khona.

Ulele ku-Yesu yena,
Apho kunga khalwa khona;
Uzuz’ ubuthongo yena,
Ange dutywe ngabo khona.

Ulele ku-Yesu zole,
Ulele njal’ elindele;
Yen ekholwa ekhangele,
Une themba elingcwele.

Ulele ku-Yesu, cwaka,
Ulele ekuphumleni;
U-Msindisi onamandla,
Uya kumbiza ngalo mhla.

Ulele ku-Yesu i-Nkos’;
Wod’ avuswe ngu-Msindisi;
Ingcwaba asiloyiki,
Lakuvulwa ngu-Mphilisi.

Ndiph’ iBhaibhile indikhanyisele, Kuze kuchwayitisw’ ohambayo;
Akunazulu elinga sifihla Ku-Yesu oweza kusindisa.

Ndiph’ iBhaibhile xa kuko usizi, Naxa umoya wam uwileyo;
Ndiphe amazwi athethwa ngu-Yesu kuze kubonw’ uMkhululi wethu.

Ndiph’ iBhaibhile eya vul’ indlela, Yabonis’ ingozi phantsi apha;
Isibane esikhanyisa kuhle, Ukuze ndimbone ndimlandele.

Ndiph’ iBhaibhile siso isibane, ’Zusiphakamise engcwabeni;
Inokukhanya okwase-zulwini, Naphesheya kwayo I-Jordane.

Phinda undihlabelele Amazw’ okuphila;
Endibon’ ubuhle bawo, Amazw’ okuphila:
Ngamazwi amahle, Aya ndifundisa.

U-Yesu wabapha bonke Amazw’ okuphila;
Moni uyabizwa, yiva Amazw’ okuphila;
Aphiwa ngesihle, Asisa ku-Yesu.

Xelela abantu bonke Amazw’ okuphila;
Azisa uxolo wona, Yes’ ungu-Msindisi;
Uya hlambulula Intliziyo zethu.

Kukh’ ilizwe elihle mpela, Sesibon’ ukukhanya kwalo;
U-Bawo wethu ukhona le, Uyasakhela izindlu ke.

Siya kuvuma kolonxweme Ingoma ze-Nkosi yaKhona;
Asoze sibone lusizi, Kwelozwe lilelokuphumla.

Ku-Bawo wethu ophezulu Saku hlokomisa ngodumo;
Ngenxa yeso sipho sothando, Nezibusiso ezaKhona.

Yiza Mthombo wosindiso, Ndikudumisa wena;
Lo misinga eyenceba Ifanel’ ukubongwa;
Ndifundis’ ukuhlonela Imfesane yaKho kum;
Izele intliziyo yam Luthando nemvuyiso.

Ndiza kuzifunela mna Ilitye lokuphila;
Ndithemba isisa saKho Ukufika ekhaya;
U-Yesu wandingenisa Emhlambini ka-Thixo,
Wandisindis’ engozini Ngalo igazi laKhe.

Ndinetyala elikhulu Ngolo fefe lwaKho kum,
Vumel’ ukulunga kwaKho Ndibuyiselwe kuWe;
Kuba ndinezono Nkosi, ndiyaziphosa kuWe;
Yiyo le intliziyo yam, Beka uphawu lwaKho.

Ndibhadule kude, Thixo, Sendibuyela;
Ndidiniwe zizono zam, Nkosi, ndiyeza.

Ndonakalise kakhulu, Sendiguquka,
Ngenyembezi ezikrakra, Nkosi, Ndamkele.

Ndidiniwe kaphambuka, ndiyabuyela;
Ndithemba uthando lwaKho, Ndiphe ufefe.

Ndinesicelo esinye, Ndiphe uYesu;
Wandifela ’ze ndiphile, Nkosi ndiyeza.

Ndihlambise namhla, Nkosi; Ndiyeza kuWe;
Ndibe mhlophe njengekhephu; Nkosi, Ndiyeza.

Mthandi womphefumlo wam, Yesu, ndiyeza kuwe,
Xa zindirhanqileyo, izilingw’ ezinkulu,
Ndisithe O Nkosi yam, Ndisithe Msindisi wam,
Ekupheleni Nkosi, Yamkela umoya wam.

Andinaso esinye isikhuselo, Yesu;
Ungandishiyi ndedwa, Uze undincede mna;
Wena, Mncedi wam, nguWe olithemba lam lonke;
Gqubuthel’ intloko yam ngawaKho amaphiko.

Ndifuna wena wedwa, Kristu, Mhlawuleli wam;
Vusa abawileyo, Philisa iziguli;
Uyingcwele ke Wena, mna ndizele kokubi,
Ndingowanyanyekayo, Uzele kukulunga.

Lwanel’ ufefe kuWe, lokundihlambulula;
Ufefe lokuhlamba, zonk’ iziphosiso zam;
Ungumthomb’ wokuphila, ndakusela ngesihle,
Hlala ngonaphakade kuyo intliziyo yam.

Yesu mthandi wentliziyo, Wena ungumthombo wobom;
Kunazo zonke izinto, Siyakukhalela thina.

Yesu, ngenyaniso yaKho, Usindisa thina boni;
Xa sifuna wena, Nkosi, Usinika ukuphumla.

Yesu, usiSonka sethu, Sinike siphile ngaSo;
Siyasela emthonjeni Ukuze saneliseke.

Yesu, sazalw’ ezonweni, Sasibanjwe ekufeni;
Sikholwa ngamandla aKho Ukusisindisa ngawo.

Yesu, wena wasifela, Wathatha ubuntu bethu;
Gxotha kuthi ubumnyama, ’Ze kuhlale ukukhanya.

Ngakumbi, ngo-Yesu iNkos’, Ndize ndifundis’ abanye.
Ndibon’ usindiso lwaKhe, Nothando londifeleyo.

Xela kwaKhona ngo-Yesu, Xela nangengqondo yaKhe;
Moya ka-Thixo ndiphe-ke, Ukwazi ngay’ u-Kristu wam.

Funda kwaKhona ngo-Yesu, Sondela ngokuthandaza;
Mamela ilizwi laKhe, Yazisa abanye ngaYe.

Ngakumbi ngo-Yes’ i-Nkosi, Ngesihlalo sobukhosi;
Lungqine udaba olo, Ngokubuya kwabangcwele.

’Zono zam zohlanjwa nja’? NguYesu ngegazi laKhe;
Ndakuba mhlophe njani? Kuphela ngegazi laKhe.

Ndibona ukuhlanjwa Egazini likaYesu;
Ukundithethelela, Kuphela ligazi laKhe.

Ndingathethelelwa na? ’Kristu nguMthetheli wethu;
Andiphethe lutho mna, Kuphela ligazi laKhe.

Lilo el’ithemba lam. Eli gazi likaYesu;
Kukho ukulunga kwam, Kuphela ligazi laKhe.

Dumo kuYe uBawo Ngeli gazi likaYesu;
Ukubonga kwam konke, Kuphela ngegazi laKhe.

Udiniwe, unomvandedwa-na? Yitsho ku-Yesu, yitsho ku-Yesu;
Unosizi olungapheliyo? Luxelele u-Yesu.

Zihla ngezidlele inyembezi? Yitsho ku-Yesu, yitsho ku-Yesu;
Unezono ezingaziwayo? Yitsho ku-Yesu yedwa.

Unosizi-na entliziyweni? Yitsho ku-Yesu, yitsho ku-Yesu;
Intliziyo yaphukile yini? Yitsho ku-Yesu yedwa.

Uyoyik’ ukucinga ngokufa? Yitsho ku-Yesu, yitsho ku-Yesu;
Ukhalela umbuso wakhe-na? Yitsho ku-Yesu yedwa.

Kumnand’ ukuthemb’ uYesu, ’Kukholwa lizwi laKhe;
Nokukwazi ukuthi ke, "Itsho njalo i-Nkosi."

Au, kumnandi ukumthemba, Ukuthemba igazi;
Ukulazi elothemba, Kusisa ku-Msindisi.

Kwo, kumnandi ukumthemba, Ukushiya izono;
Ukuthemba owajinga, Kusinika uxolo.

Ndifunde ukukuthemba, Yesu wena Msindisi;
Ndiyazi unam ngenene, Kude kube nanini.

Suk’ oluhle lokukhetha Wena Thixo, U-Msindisi;
Kumnandi intliziyo yam, ivuyele ezo ndaba.

Kuphelile, kuphelile, NdingoweNkos’ yona yeyam.
Indirhola ndilandele, Nal’ ubizo olungcwele.

Mayiphumle intliziyo, Icamange ngezi zinto;
Ingaz’ imke eNkosini, Ezaliswe kukulunga

Izifungo endinazo Zohlaziywa onk’ amaxa;
Kude kuphele imihla Yokuphila emhlabeni.

Xa ebuya uMsindisi Ezok’thabath’ abangcwele,
Ndakulawula neNkosi yam, Kwelo khaya laphezulu.

hymns.chorus:
Awu! Luhle usuku, Wandihlamb’ izon’ uYesu;
Wandibiza, sendivile, Ndinovuyo, ndigcobile,
Awu! Luhle usuku, Wandihlamb’ izon’ uYesu.

Masiye e-Ziyon’ Au! Ubuhle be-Ziyoni;
Tenor &amp; Bass: Masiye khon’ eZiyon.
Siya singisa phezulu, Umzi omhle oka-Thixo.

hymns.lyrics:
Mna sendakhululwa ngegazi! Ndakhululwa nguYesu ke;
Ndakhululwa ngalo ufefe, SendikuYe naphakade.

Mna ngo-Yesu ndivuyisiwe, Ngoku kukho uvuyo kum;
Oko kukhanya kwaKhe kunam, Ngokuba ndazuzwa nguYe.

Ndakumkhumbula u-Msindisi, Ndicamange ngaYe njalo;
Ndakucula ndingathi cwaka, Ndimbonge ngothando lwaKhe.

KuYesu ndiyazi ndobona U-Msindisi onothando;
Undigcina endikhusela, Undipha ingom’ emnandi.

Isithsaba sindilindele Kwelo khaya liphezulu;
Kufuphi nabangcwele kanye, Ndakuba naYe phezulu.

Siya kuphumla emanzini Awase mthonjeni;
U-Yesu wehla ezulweini, Wema emhlabeni.

Xa sidiniwe kuku-hamba, Kumnand’ ukuphumla,
Apho amanzi entyiloza, Apho sakuhlamba.

Yizani ke ku-Yesu Kristu, Wonipha amandla;
Nguye amanzi okuphila, Sela unganxanwa.

Xa uYesu abutha’ izizwe, Zize zime phambi kwaKhe;
Siyakubonakala njani, Ukwamkela isigwebo?

Uza kutsho na u-Msindisi, "Heke, Mkhonzi olungileyo?"
Ingaba ke sothuthumela, ’Ze sigxothwe simke kuYe?

Uyabagcobela bon’ abaKhe, Abo banophawu lwaKhe;
Uyabanxibisa ngobuhle, xa Sebequbudile kuYe.

Masimlindele u-Msindisi Sineziban’ ezivuthayo;
X’ umyeni efika ebusuku, Masilunge ’ze simbone.

Ngentliziyo ebheka phezulu, Kwanangokunyamezela,
Xa sesilugqibile uhambo, Sakubon’ ubuso baKhe.

Nkos’ andinanze mfuyo yalo eli lizwe;
Ndikhalel’ ukungena khon’ ezulwini;
Encwadini yombuso waKho ezulwini,
Ndixelele Msindisi othandekayo kum.

Nkosi, ezi zono zam zinje ngentlabathi;
Kodwa igazi laKho lanele kumoni;
Kuba isithembiso saKho sibhaliwe,
"Ndozihlamba izono zaKho zibe mhlophe."

Kumzi okhazimlayo one zindlw’ ezintle,
Kukho ke abangcwele bane ngub’ ezintle,
Akungeni izinto ezingcolileyo,
Kuhleli izithunywa ezilindileyo.

Amasimi alindile, Amhlophe ngamazimba;
Nakude siwabonile, Nase khaya anjalo.

Bathume kwasekuseni, Namalanga bangemi;
Nokuba kuse mnyameni, Mabavun’ entsimini.

Wen’ uthunywayo yi-Nkosi Vuna ungaKhohlisi;
’Moya wakhe ngu-Mphathisi Koyayo ku-Msindisi.

Sebenza kuz’ ukuhlwa, Sebenza emini,
Xa umbethe usekho, ’Ntyatyamb’ iphuma;
Nokukhanya kusekho, Sebenza emini,
Sebenza kuz’ ukuhlwa, Konke kophela.

Sebenza kuz’ ukuhlwa, Liyatshon’ ilanga;
Sebenz’ imini yonke, Ungalibali;
Yenza kuzale konke kungashiyeki nto;
Sebenza kuz’ ukuhlwa, Konke kophela.

Sebenza kuz’ ukuhlwa, Ayez’ amathunzi;
Phaya entshonalanga Lihlil’ ilanga;
Qina sekuya phela, Zama ukhuthale;
Kuba kuyez’ ukuhlwa, Konke kophela.

Nkosi ekuseni yiva Ukukucenga kwam;
KuWe ndiza kuthandaza, Ndokhangela kuWe.

Phambi koBawo ekhaya Siyathethelelwa,
U-Yesu uzisa kuYe Izicelo zethu.

Nditsale ngoMoya waKho, Endleleni yaKho;
Konke oku kuhamba kwam Kuqondise kuhle.

Abathanda wena, Yesu, Baza kukholiswa;
U-Thixo ngofefe lwaKhe Abagqubuthele.

O ukutsholoza ngalo Igama layo i-Nkosi;
Bubukhosi obunjalo, Igama layo i-Nkosi.

Yesu amandla akulo, Igama layo i-Nkosi;
Yingoma yokuhlatyelwa, Igama layo i-Nkosi.

Liphelisa konk’ ukona, Igama layo i-Nkosi;
Lithembekile ke lona, Igama layo i-Nkosi.

Vuma amandla ka-Thixo Adala intaba,
Nolwandle walwaneka ke, Nesibhakabhaka;
Ndihlabela ubulumko Obenza ilanga,
Nenyanga yas’ ebusuku, kunye nenkwenkwezi.

Hlabela ngofefe kuYe Osipha ukudla;
Wadala ngelizwi laKhe Konke emhlabeni;
Sibon’ imimangaliso Macaleni onke,
Khona apha emhlabeni, Nase zulwini le.

Onke amabali apha Ayangqina ngaYe;
Amafu nomoya kunye Ahlonel’ uMenzi;
’Zidalwa ziphila ngaYe, Uya ziphaphela;
Singabalekela phina? i-Nkosi ikhona.

Dumisa iNkosi eyingcwele,
Bonga ngothando lwaY’ olukhulu;
Likhaka lethu, U-Nyangelemihla,
Ohlala ebuhleni obungcwele.

Xela ngothando, vuma ngofefe,
Owambeth’ ukukhanya phezulu;
Xa izulu liduma qondisisa,
Indlela, yaKhe inokoyikeka.

Ukondla kwaKho, nguban’ ongatsho!
Kusemhlotsheni kuse moyeni;
Kuya qukuqela ezintabeni,
Kuyithoba imvula nemibethe.

Singabantwana bothuli thina;
KuWe sinethemb’ elinamandla;
Au! Inceba nothando lwaKho kuthi!
Sihlobo, Mkhuseli wethu, Somandla!

Bawo siza kuWe, AkaKho ongomnye;
Uyinqaba yethu, Themba lethu;
Umhlaba umnyama xa ungekho wena;
Yiz’ usithuthuzel’ O, Msindisi

Sisindise thina Kuzo zonk’ intshaba;
Ungu-Mthetheli no-Mhlawuleli;
Thina siyoyika; Siqinise Bawo,
Ngengalo yegazi, Sisindise.

Siph’ inceba yaKho, Nelo lizwi laKho;
Nenyawo zethu ziqondisise.
O, sikhokele Nkos’ Size S’yokuwela,
Sibe ngaphesheya Ezulwini.

Kumnandi ukuthandaza, Kundibiz’ elusizini;
Kundibikela ku-Bawo, Konke oku kuswela kwam;
Ngamaxesha enkathazo Ndizuza ukupholiswa;
Andiwole ngamaphiko, Ngomoya wokuthandaza.

Kumnandi ukuthandaza, Kundithwalel’ izicelo,
Aze Othembekileyo andisikelele Yena;
Uthi mandicinge ngaYe, Mandikholwe lizwi laKhe;
Uyakundinceda Yena, Ndakulinda ndithandaze.

Kumnandi ukuthandaza Ngathi ndiyathuthuzelwa,
Ndize ndibone ikhaya, Ndiye kulo ndinoxolo;
Ndakuhamba ndifun’ izwe Elingenaz’ iinkathazo;
Ndimemeze, ndimemeze, "Sala kuhle Kuthandaza."

Kuphelil’ ukusebenza, Sesiqala i-Sabatha;
Yiza Moy’ uzokuvuya Ngolusuku walukhetha.

Yiza sibonge i-Nkosi Ngokuphumla okumnandi;
Intsikelelo mawethu Zabekwa nguy’ u-Mkhululi.

Zingathi ezingcamango Zethu zibonge u-Thixo;
Ukuze yen’ okholwayo Amkelisw’ okwabhalwayo.

Ukuvuy’ entliziyweni Kulithemba emhlabeni,
Elanikwa ebandleni, Lavela kuY’ ezulwini.

Lindani i-Nkosi, Iya biza namhla;
Lindani niqine, Lindani ma-Kristu;
Qinani nilinde, ’Tshaba lunamandla,
Thembani ku-Yesu, Linda ningadinwa.

Gxothani okubi, Lahlan’ ukusola,
Umvuzo ngowenu, Ekhay’ ezulwini;
Lindani maKholwa, Nalindwa ngu-Kristu,
Uyanazi nonke, Nithengwe ngegazi.

Thembani ku-Yesu, Thandazani kuYe,
Hloman’ izikhali, Nilinde i-Nkosi;
Xa ubon’ ilanga, Ungalibali ke;
Ngalo elixesha, Linda, Mkristu, linda.

Ninga yilibali i-Sabatha ye-Nkosi;
Yiyon’ intle kunawo onke amalanga;
Yiyona isiphumz’ emisebenzini yethu,
Ivula ukukhanya, Okwasezulwini.

Gcinan’ i-Sabatha, dumisani Yena,
Owathi "Ndiyindlela yokuphila kuni."
Xa simlandela Yena u-Msindisi apha,
Uya kusiph’ amanzi okuphila Yena.

Langa elingcwele! Ngawe siya bonga;
U-Yesu ungumhlobo wethu othandwayo;
Wena Msindisi wethu unenceba nothando.
Izithembisa zaKho zikukuvuyisa.

Usilondolozile ngale veki u-Thixo;
Masicele endlwini intsikelelo kuYe;
Usuku kuzo zonke oluhle ezintsuku,
Usuku kuzo zonke oluhle ezintsuku.

Xa sicela inceba ngegama lo-Msindisi,
Sibonile ubuso baKho, usisindise;
Siphe namhla siphuml’ e-misebenzini yethu,
Siphe namhla siphuml’ e-misebenzini yethu.

Size apha igama laKho ukudumisa;
Khona apha namhlanje masiv’ udumo lwaKho;
Siphe njalo sibekho aph’ esidlweni saKho,
Siphe njalo sibekho aph’ esidlweni saKho.

Mayimenyezwe kubo aboni iVangeli,
Ibe nentuthuzelo kwazabo iintliziyo,
Ukuze i-Sabatha zethu zibe zezintle,
’De sivuke ngalo mhla siy’ ezulwini kuWe.

Siyavuya ngalo mhla Owasikelelwayo;
Siwamkela ngovuyo, Ngokwelanga lezulu.

Lilanga lokuphumla, Lihamba kuhl’ ixesha;
Sithuthuzelwa ngalo, Kude kuphel’ ubomi.

Min’ engcwele enkulu, Yokubonga iNkosi,
Sifunda ngawo lo mhla, Ngentsikelelo zaKho.

Siyavuya ngalo mhla, Neempembelelo zawo;
Sivula nentliziyo, Siphe uMoya waKho.

Sive ngesand’ esihle, U-Yesu, U-Yesu;
Yen’ uyasisindisa, U-Yesu, U-Yesu.
Yazis’ izizwe zonke, Naphesheyo kolwandle,
I-Nkos’ iyasithuma, NgoYesu, NgoYesu.

Bongani, Dumisani, U-Yesu, U-Yesu;
Baxelelwe abone, NgoYesu, NgoYesu.
Vuman’ eziqithini, Sabela nawe lwandle,
Ngazo indab’ ezintle, NguYesu, NguYesu.

Xelelan’ abalwayo, NgoYesu, NgoYesu;
Wafa waza waphila, U-Yesu, U-Yesu;
Xelan’ indab’ emnandi, Kwabadakumbileyo;
’Ngcwaba uloyisile, U-Yesu, U-Yesu.

Phosan’ emoyen’ izwi, NgoYesu, NgoYesu;
Vuyani nonke zizwe, NgoYesu, NgoYesu.
Khwazani usindiso Ezintabeni zonke,
Ingoma yoloyiso KaYesu, KaYesu.

Ndiyamfuna u-Msindisi, Ngekhe ndihambe ndedwa;
Mandihambe endleleni, Endibambe ngesandla.

Ndiyamfuna u-Msindisi, Ndedwa ndakulahleka;
Nguye yena u-Mvuyisi, kade ndisoyiseka.

Ndiyamfuna u-Msindisi Kuko ukuhamba kwam;
Abaninzi banosizi, Yiba ungu-Mncedi wam.

Ndiyamfuna u-Msindisi, Uyayazi indlela;
Ndakumlandel’ u-Msindisi, Weza ukusifela.

Ndakuqwalasel’ i-krusi, Ekwaxhonyw’ eyam i-Nkosi;
Ndoncama yonk’ inzuzo yam, Ndilidelel nekratshi lam.

Bonan’ intloko nezandla, Kunye nawo amanxeba,
Akrazulwa ngenxa yethu; Yeka! Uthand’ olungaka!

Nda ndiyawalahlekile; Ndazuz’ ukuthethelelwa;
Yala, ndingaziqhayisi Kodwa kube ngomnqamlezo.

Zonk’ indyebo endinazo Zingumnikelo omncinci;
Ngenxa yothand’ olungaka Ndinikela impilo yam.

U-Yesu ukubizel’ ekhaya - Uya biza kanye namhla;
Ilanga lothando ulishiya, uya usimka ngani?

Abadiniweyo ubabiza - Uya biza kanye namhla;
Mnik’ umthwalo akusikelele; Akasoku kugxotha.

Yiza ngoku, ulindele wena - Uya linda kanye namhla;
Yiza nezon’ uzithobe kuye; Yiza, m’sukulibala.

Uya kucenga, Au! Mphulaphule - Uya cenga, yiva namhla;
Abo baKholwayo bakuvuya; Khauleza usabise.

Nank’ umhambi emnyango, M’angene; (Mvumel’ angene; Mvumel’ angene);
Sekufuthi ebaKho, M’angene; (Mvumel’ angene; Mvumel’ angene);
M’angene enge kemki, M’ angene engo-Ngcwele,
U-Krist’ u-Nyan’ o-Yise, M’angene. (Mvumel’ angene, Mvumel’ angene).

Mnik’ intliziyo yaKho, M’angene; (Mvumel’ angene; Mvumel’ angene);
Lumka hlez’ akushiye, M’angene; (Mvumel’ angene; Mvumel’ angene);
Ungum hlob’ aKho yena, Uya kukukhusela,
Kube sekupheleni, M’angene. (Mvumel’ angene, Mvumel’ angene).

Yiva, uyakucenga, M’angene; (Mvumel’ angene; Mvumel’ angene);
Nyula yena ngokunje, M’angene; (Mvumel’ angene; Mvumel’ angene);
Nank’ emi ngase mnyango, Wokunika uvuyo,
Ukhung’ igama lakhe; M’angene. (Mvumel’ angene, Mvumel’ angene).

Vum’ ummenywa wezulu, M’angene; (Mvumel’ angene; Mvumel’ angene);
Wokwenzela isidlo; M’angene; (Mvumel’ angene; Mvumel’ angene);
Akuxolel’ izono, Kothi ekupheleni,
Akuse ezulwini, M’angene. (Mvumel’ angene, Mvumel’ angene).

Ndiyakhala ndibabale ngoku, Yiza-ke Mkhululi;
Ndiya kulangazelela Wena, Yiza-ke Mkhululi.

Andinas’ ikhusel’ ebusuku, Yiza-ke Mkhululi;
Wakukhangela ndoba nobomi, Yiza-ke Mkhululi.

Ndihamba indlel’ enobunzima, Yiza-ke Mkhululi;
Amehlo am akhangele kuWe, Yiza-ke Mkhululi.

Akusal’ isingqala somoni, Yiza-ke Mkhululi;
Ndithandaza yiv’ isikhalo sam, Yiza-ke Mkhululi.

Ndibalisele ngo-Yesu, Bhal’ entliziyweni yam,
Ibal’ elinexabiso, Elona linencasa;
Yathin’ intsholo ye-ngelos’ mini wazalwa yena,-
Dumo ku-Thix’, enyangweni, Uvuyo kulomhlaba.

Wazila yedwa entlango, Xela ngayo lomihla.
Entlango apho wehendwa, wapheta ngokoyisa;
Xel’ iminyak’ esebenza, Iminyaka yosizi,
Wadelwa, wabandezelwa, Wagxothwa elusizini.

Khautsho ngokumxhom’ emthini, Encwina enentlungu;
Hi ngengcwaba waba kulo, Hi wabuya waphila;
Uthando kuyo lombali, Lundibengezelela,
Hlala noko ndililayo, Uthando lwandithenga.

Ngexesha lokuvavanywa, kunikw’ okwaphakade;
Soba njenge-golide-na, Mhlawumbi njengo-thuli?

Soweva-n’anje amazwi, "He-ke, tyaphile";
Mhlawumb’ isigwebo sokufa, "Moni uyalambatha?"

U-Moya uya sicenga, Isekho-nje inceba,
Lumka wabhala u-Thixo, Egweba bona bonke.

Waven’ amazwi om-Sindisi, Amazwi obom ngenene;
Nqenerha ’kuthandaza, phulaphula, ’Yes’ uthi, "Thamsanqa kubenzi."

’Fumana siv’ amazwi aKhe, Kwa nalomadinga aKhe;
’Kuweva, koyikwe, kunge sindisi, Luyolo, luyolo kubenzi.

Ngovuyo bongena emzini, Singekh’ isono nosizi;
Bangcwele, ’zukile ngonaphakade, Benegunya kumthi wobomi.

Kukh’ ubom ukubhek’ emnqamlezwen’ Yesu uthe, "bhekani Kum";
Luthuth’ ubutyebi bomhlaba, Ndibon’ indyebo emnqamlezweni.

Ngomhl’ endabona ngaw’ um-Sindisi, Wancum’ akundikhangela;
Kuthi ndakuwelwa kuhendwa, Ndibhek’ emnqamlezweni ndisinde.

Ndohlala ndikhangel’ umnqamlezo, Ndithemb’ idingal’ka-Thixo;
Um-hendi ’zange amoyise Lowo uthemb’ amandla ezulu.

U-Yes’ uyabiza ngezwi lenceba, Uyabiza, wena nam;
Ulind’ elucangweni lwentliziyo, Ulindele wena nam.

Simeleni xa u-Yes’ esicenga, Ebongozela thina?
Masingahilizel’ inceba zakhe, Ezenza ngenxa yethu.

Laphela ixesha, yemk’ imizuzu, Likushiya wena nam;
Amathunz’ okufa ayasondela, Afika kuwe nakum.

Cinga ngothando aludingileyo, Eludinge wena nam;
Sonile use nenceba noxolo, Uxolo kuwe nakum.

Kukh’ ucang’ oluvul’ weyo, Kwisango elinomtha;
Ovela emnqamlezweni, Utyhil’ uthando lweNkos’.

Cango luvulelwe bonke, Abafun’ usindiso;
Zizonk’ iindidi zabantu, Zonk’ izizwe nentlanga.

Thyobozan’ elutshabeni, Ngoku kusavuliwe;
Nas’ isithsaba silwelen, Siluphau lothando.

Phesheya komlambo sobek’ Iminqamlezo yethu,
Sithwal’ isithsaba sobom, Somthanda ezulwini.

U-Gqir’ omkhul’ ukufuphi, u-Yes’ onovelwano;
Evus’ intliziy’ ewayo, Yiv’ izwi lika-Yesu!

Zonk’ izono zixolelwe, Yiv’ izwi lika-Yesu;
Yiy’ ezulwin’ unoxolo, Uthweswe isithsaba.

Lonke uzuko kwi-Mvana! NdiyaKholwa ku-Yesu;
Eligama ndilithanda, Igama lika-Yesu!

Ligxotha lonk’ ivuso lam; Akukho gama limbi;
Luyolo kumphefumlo wam, Igama lika-Yesu!

Nangex’ eza nesithsaba, -esobomi nozuko;
Sothi-ke sihlale naYe, Sibalis’ ukhululo.

Nal’ iliza elibomvu, Linzulu, libanzi;
U-Yes’ onokusindisa, Walath’ enxebeni.

Ndibon’ ukudalw’ okutsha, Ndiv’ izwi legazi;
Lithetha--kuf’ ukungcola, Kutshon’ egazini.

Ndihamba ekukhanyeni, Ngaphezu kwesono;
’Ngubo zam zenziwe mhlophe Ngu-Kristu i-Nkosi.

Simanga solu babalo, Lwenziwe ngegazi,
Ngu-Yesu yedw’ owaziyo, U-Yes’ obethelwe.

Ndolula izandla, Bawo; Ndincedwa nguWe mna;
Xa wen’ uzirhoxisa kum, Awu, ndoya ngaphi na?

Ndikholwa kuNyana waKho, Ndinike amandla;
Ndikhulul’ ezintsweleni Ngale yure yaKho.

Mdal’ wokholo, amehlo am Akhangela kuWe;
Ndamkelise eso sipho, Singekho ndifile.

Akungendiyeki ndife, Thetha ’ze ndiphile;
Ndolinda apha ngomonde, Ndizuze uMoya.

Ndovuyiswa yini, Nkosi, Xa ungekho wena?
Thetha izwi lempiliso, Ndize ndixolelwe.

NdiyaKholwa kaloku nje, ’Yesu wandifela;
Wandiphalazel’ igazi, Ndakhululw’ esonwen’

hymns.chorus:
Lelona lingcwele (lingcwele), lelona lingcwele (lingcwele);
Laphuma ku-Yise lez’ emhlaben’ Leza nezithunywa,
Ngexa lobusuku (busuku),  Elogama lika-Yesu.

hymns.lyrics:
Makadume u-Kristu, ingabi ndim;
Makaviwe u-Kristu abonwe;
Kuzo zonk’ izenzo ibe ngu-Kristu,
Ibe nguYe ngengcina nangezwi.

Entsizini makandithuthuzele,
Azisule zonk’ inyembezi zam;
Andithwalise umthwal’ osindayo,
Alugxothe lonke uloyiko.

Kristu yedwa! Ingabi gama limbi,
Kristu yedwa; ndingazikhathazi;
Kristu yedwa; ndingaziphakamisi;
Kristu yedwa, "mna" asithele tu.

NguKristu ondixhase intswelo zam;
NguKristu yedwa ongamandla am;
NguKristu yedwa ogcine konk’ okwam;
Kristu yedwa kube phakade.

Kuya khanya encotsheni, Kuya khanya elwandle,
Ilele imith’ ebomvu engceni yesihlambo;
Kanti olona lukhanyo Luzalis’ intliziyo;
Kuba aph’ aKhon’ u-Kristu, Kukho ukhanyiselo.

Ndilushiy’ olwam usizi, Ngokwengubo endala,
Undambese ngokugcoba, Ndizele yindumiso;
Nakwelo khaya lozuko Undizuzele lona,
Ndinyusa ngentliziyo yam, ulandel’ umoya wam.

Ndithengwe ngum-Sindisi wam, Konk’ okwam kuko kwaKhe;
Isiban’ osilumeke Masizukise wena;
Nasekhayeni lozuko Ondizuzele lona,
Ndinyusa ngentliziyo yam Ulandel’ umoya wam.

Ndinengoma yokuvuma Yokukhululwa kwam;
Ngum-Sindisi, Kumkani wam, Endikhulule-nje.

Undihluthis’ u-Kristu wam, Ngokundikhulula;
’Ntando yakhe libhaso lam, Endikhulula-nje.

Ubungqina bucacile, Bokukhululwa kwam;
Buchith’ amathandabuzo, Nokoyika konke.

Undibekel’ ikhaya lam, Endikhulula-nje;
Ndohlala ngonaphakade, Endikhulula-nje.

hymns.chorus:
Ndingo khululweyo, Ndingokhululweyo,
Dumo Kwigama laKhe;
Ndingo khululweyo, Ndomdumisa um-Sindisi wam.

hymns.lyrics:
Xa awayo ugqatyana, ’Thix’ umkathalele;
Ezithanda-nje intaka, Uya ndithanda nam.

Uhombisa inyibiba, Abuyi ayiqhole;
Ethanda intyatyambo-nje, uya ndithanda nam.

Zenziwa ngu-Thixo zonke, Ngobukhulu bazo;
Kwa nab’ abantwana bakhe Uba thanda bonke.

Nge-yure yomthandazo, Sithob’ intliziyo,
Sihlangana ku-Yesu, Umhlobo wethu;
Size kuye ngokholo, Az’ asikhusele,
Aphuml’ odiniweyo! Ath’ ukuba mnandi!

Nge-yure yomthandazo, Ukufuphi nathi,
Ezele yimfesane ebantwaneni;
Uthi masiwaphose Amaxhala kuYe;
Aphuml’ odiniweyo! Ath’ ukuba mnandi!

Nge-yure yomthandazo, Xa olingiweyo
Aya kum-Sindisi Omthanda kakhulu,
Wothi onovelwano Agxoth’ amaxhala;
Aphuml’ odiniweyo! Ath’ ukuba mnandi!

Nge-yure yomthandazo, Simkholelwa Yena,
Wosixhasa ngazo zonk’ intsikelelo;
Sizele lelithemba, Soba msulw’ exhalen’;
Aphuml’ odiniweyo! Ath’ ukuba mnandi!

Wena Yes’ udinge Abo bambalwa
Bathe bahlangana, Nawe wobaKho;
Sikholwa li-Lizwi, Siya thandaza;
Yiz’ uthamsanqele, Nkosi zityhile.

Ngawo amaxesha Awadlulayo
Wamana unathi, Solok’ unathi;
Yiza O Msindisi, Usibabale;
Sive usamkele Ekuthandazen’.

Hlab’ amazwi ethu Akudumise;
Sive xa sicela Sijonge kuWe;
Qinisa ukholo Khanyis’ ithemba;
Lube nyul’ uthando, Nendlel’ icace.

NdingowaKho Nkos’, ndiv’ izwi laKho Lixel’ uthando lwaKho;
Ndingavuka ngengalo zokholo, ndibe kufuphi naWe.

Ndingcwalisel’ inkonzo yaKho Nkos’ Ngegunya lobungcwele;
Gxumek’ ithemba lomphefumlo wam, Ulaule intando yam.

Au ubunyulu bexa elinye Endiba kuWe ngalo,
’Ze ndithandaze kuWe Thixo wam, Njengomhlobo kumhlobo!

Nzulu zothando endinge zazi Ndide ndidlul’ ulwandle;
Apho ndingeze ndifikelele Ndide ndiphumle nawe.

Ndingaba njengo-Yesu; O Msindisi, hlala nam,
Ngoxolo nangothando, Ndenze ndikuthobele;
Ndithi xa ndihambayo, Khona aph’ elizweni;
Ndibe hlwempu ngomoya--O, Msindisi hlala nam.

Ihlungul’ eliva-nje, kanjalo uyambona,
Nonqhatyana x’ awayo, ’Nene wosabela kum,
Yena wondifundisa, Andixolele konke;
Ndinga ndingaba nyulu--O, Msindisi hlala nam.

Ndingaba njengo-Yesu, Xa ndithandazayo nam;
Ndiphumle ndingakuYe, Kumlamb’ ozolileyo;
Ndizelwe nguYe ’kutsha, Ndivum’ intando yaKhe;
Ndingatyeba ngokholo--O, Msindisi hlala nam

Kufuphi nomnqamlezo, Khona kukh’ umlambo;
Ophuma e-Kalvari, Ophilisa bonke.

Kufuphi nomnqamlezo, Ndafuman’ inceba;
Apho i-Khwezi lo-Mso, Lindi khanyisela.

Kufuphi nomnqamlezo, O-Mvana ka-Thixo,
Ndisibekele ngaso, Isithunzi sawo.

Kufuphi nomnqamlezo, Likhon’ ithemba lam;
Ndide ndifikelele, Phesheya komlambo.

Ndihambe naWe, Thixo wam, Njengay’ u-Enok’ mandulo;
Ndibambe wena ngesandla, Uze-ke udlelane nam;
Nax’ indlela isithele, Yesu, mandihambe naWe.

Ndingekhe ndihambe ndedwa, Luvuthuza uqhwithela;
Inyawo zam zithiyelwe, Ndilalelwe zintshaba zam;
Zolis’ ugqumo lolwandle; O Mongameli, hamba nam.

Xa ndibambelele kuWe, Andiw’ nanzi ngant’ umhlaba,
Ndohamba ndikhaliphile; Ndithwel’ indwe yomnqamlezo;
Ndide ndibon’ i-Ziyoni; Msindisi wam, ’zu hambe nam.

Ngentlokoma ephakame Umphefumlo wam uvuma;
Uphina kodwa ovuma Ngothand’ olungummangaliso?

Emini nase busuku, Luluxolo nokuzola,
Luliyeza kwa namandla, Lona uthando luka-Yesu.

Ndakubiza, ndixolelwa, Ndakuwa ndiphakanyiswe;
Ebomini nasekufen’ Lunjal’ uthando luka-Yesu.

Ndikuthanda ngakumbi, Nkos’, Nakumgcobo wonke;
Kuba undfinik’ uxolo Olunge bulawe.

Ndiyaz’ usondele wena Kunomhlaba wonke;
Kumnand’ ukucinga ngawe Kunengoma zonke.

Uvuyis’ intliziyo yam; Ndogcoba ke ngoko;
Ngaphandle kothando lwaKho Ndise lusizini.

Msindisi onexabiso! Xa wena ukhoyo,
Luz’ ugcobo longamele Sihamba sinawe.

Wonk’ umhlaba awunto kum, Kunye novuyo lwawo;
Ndiph’ u-Yesu abe ngowam, Kuse ephakadeni.

Wonk’ umhlaba awunto kum, Wonwabil’ umphefumlo;
Ndilindwa ngum-Sindisi wam, Ndivum’ ingom’ emnandi.

Wonk’ umhlaba awunto kum, Ndimbon’ u-Yes’ encuma;
Nakulo oluhambo lwam, Ndivuyiswa kukhanya.

Wonk’ umhlaba awunto kum, Xa ndihlel’ emnqamlezwen’;
Ndide ndimbone ubuso, Ubuso be-Nkosi yam.

Nkosi nab’ ubomi bam, Ndibunikela wena,
Nanzi kwa nezandla zam, Zisebenzise wena.

Nkosi nanz’ inyawo zam, Zinamend’ okukhonza;
Nali nezwi lengoma, Kuye u-Kumkani wam.

Nkosi Nang, umlomo wam, Uzel’ udaba lwaKho;
Nantsi kwa nendyebo yam,--Iyonke yeyaKho Nkos’.

Nkosi nants’ imihla yam, Ndikudumise ngayo;
Nantsi kwa nengqondo yam, Yenza ngegunya laKho.

Nkosi nants’ intando yam, Ayisobe ibe yam;
Nantsi nentliziyo yam, Yenz’ isihlalo saKho.

Nkosi nal’ uthando lwam, Loba yindyebo yaKho;
Nabu nab’ ubuntu bam, Zonke ngonaphakade.

O, ndimfumene u-Mhlobo! Wandithanda ndingamaz’;
Ngothando wanditsala mna, Wandibophela kuye.
Yathi nalentliziyo yam Wakwa yiqamangela,
Ngoko-ke ndingowakhe mna Kuse ephakadeni.

O, ndimfumene u-Mhlobo! Nguy’ owandifelayo;
Wandenzel’ isipho sobom, Ngabo ubomi bakhe.
Izinto zam asizo zam, Zezakhe ongum-Niki;
Mandla, bomi, konke okwam, Zizezakhe nanini.

O, ndimfumene u-Mhlobo! Onk’ amandla ngawakhe;
Nakulo oluhambo lwam, Wondisa ezulwini.
Ndibon’ ubuqaqawuli, Bundinika amandla;
Ngoku xa ndise dabini, Ndizakuthi ndiphumle.

O, ndimfumene u-Mhlobo! O’bubele nenceba,
Um-Khokeli osilumko, Um-Khusel’ onamandla.
Kowandithanda kakuhle, Ndingahlulwa yhintoni?
Bubomi-na, sihogo-na? Ngu-notshe; ndingowakhe.

Lith’ ilizwi lika-Yesu, "Yiza kum uphumle;
Hlala wen’ udiniweyo, Esifubeni sam."
Ndiza ku-Yesu ndinjalo--Ndijacwe lusizi;
Kukh’ ukuphumla kuye lo, Uya ndivuyisa.

Lith’ ilizwi lika-Yesu, "Yabona ndikupha;
Amanzi agqib’ unxano, Thoba uwasele."
Ndize ku-yesu ndasela, Kulomlambo wobom;
Laphel’ unxano lwam lonke, Ngok’ ndiphila kuYe.

Lith’ ilizwi lika-Yesu, "Ndilukhanyiselo.
Bheka kum, ukhanyiselwe, Uqaqambe njalo."
Ndenze njalo, ndafumana Ukhanyo lwelanga;
Ndohamba kolo khanyo ke, Ndide ndilufeze.

Ndinga ndingaba ngowaKho, Nkos’; Yiz’ undifundise;
Ndinga ndingenz’ intando yaKho; Ndincede ngoku.

Bonke ubutyebi nodumo Buyinton’ ungekho?
Ndishiya konke ngenxa yaKho, u-Butyebi bam.

Ndizilahla zonk’ iziyolo, Yiza kufuphi nam;
Ndizifumana zonke kuwe, Ndize ndonwabe.

Sindulule kaloku Nkos’, Sizalise ngovuyo;
Usinik’ uthando lwaKho, Singabathengwa baKho.
Sihlaziye, sihlaziye, sihamba kule ntlango!

Sikubulela, sikhunga, Ngentsholo ye-vangeli;
Iziqhamo zosindiso, Maziqaqambe kuthi;
Sithembeke, sithembeke, Sikuyo lenyaniso.

Logama sise selizwen’, Silaule Nkosi yethu;
Someleze ngelo themba, Sihambe singadinwa
Side silubon’ uzuko Sinawe ezulwini.

Indlela yam iyenyuka, Yonk’ imihla iyenyuka;
Ndithandaza onk’ amaxa, "Nkosi mandityalwe nguWe."

Andithandi kuhlal’ apho Kukho amathandabuzo;
Noxa bambi bangahlala, Ndise kumhlab’ ophezulu.

Mandiphile ndikhuselwe Kwezo ntolo zika-Sathan;
Kub’ ukholo lwenz’ intsholo, Kwingoma yabo bangcwele.

Ndinqwenela ukuntinga ’Ze ndibone olozuko;
Ndithandazela izulu, "Ndiphakamise Nkosi yam."

Mus’ ukwala wena, Umsebenzi mkhulu;
Yiba ulungele Ixa lokuthunywa.
Yena ngobubele Usel’ ekumema,
Uthixo wezulu Uthuma wena lo.

Mus’ ukwala wena, Ubizwa namhlanje;
Kukade usala, Ngoku ngxama wenze.
Amasim’ amhlophe, Bambalw’ abavuni;
Wuvuyele ngoko Umsebenzi we-Nkos’.

Mus’ ukwala wena, Yingoz’ ukunqena;
Lwalus’ oluthando, Hleze lumke mpela.
Isekho nj’ inceba, Walathisw’ exulwin’.
U-Yes’ ukumele, Yiza uxolelwe!

Nditsalele kuwe Bawo wam, Mandiwolwe nguWe;
Undisongel’ ezingalweni, Ndifun’ ukuphumla.

Nditsalele kuWe, Msindisi, Sobe ndikushiye;
Mandiziv’ iingalo zaKho kum, Sobe ndihilize.

Nditsale, Moya oyiNgcwele, Mandifane naWe;
